h2 Create Team

div.instructions Create a team record in SportsHerd for the following Facebook Group

h3 Facebook Group
img(src='http://graph.facebook.com/#{facebookGroupId}/picture?type=large')
div: label Team Name
div: input#name(value='#{name}')

div.status

div
  input.cancel(type='button', value='Cancel')
  input.next(type='button', value='Create Team')